WEBVTT

00:01:58.792 --> 00:02:00.392
But things have changed.

00:02:01.014 --> 00:02:02.934
Over the last five years,

00:02:02.958 --> 00:02:07.367
computers and graphics cards
have gotten seriously fast.

00:02:08.508 --> 00:02:12.479
And machine learning,
deep learning, has happened.

00:02:13.408 --> 00:02:14.641
So we asked ourselves:

00:02:15.320 --> 00:02:19.098
Do you suppose we could create
a photo-realistic human,

00:02:19.122 --> 00:02:20.746
like we're doing for film,

00:02:21.932 --> 00:02:27.579
but where you're seeing
the actual emotions and the details

00:02:27.603 --> 00:02:31.680
of the person who's controlling
the digital human